The body has been handed over to the South African Police Service for further investigation. CAPE TOWN - The body of a man who fell to his death on Table Mountain has been recovered.It's been handed over to the South African Police Service for further investigation.Wilderness Search and Rescue's Johann Marais says he fell from near Maclear's Beacon. He fell into Platteklip Gorge and landed very close to the footpath. (Edited by Zamangwane Shange)